Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的伙伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}似乎顺利溜进来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这也在老师的算计之中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}毕竟这样似乎更有趣些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是打输了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}春花你们不就会死了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们是不可能会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呀 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您不是能说话么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还是不要小看半藏学院…“雾夜”比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每当学生战败都会分析反省其败因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}克服弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}扬长避短
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这点必会被确实履行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们是为了锻炼半藏学院的学生才与她们作战至今的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们是我最强的忍者学生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}必须要有与你们相配的对手才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的目的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管你的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但老师您毕竟是将我从地狱中拯救出来的恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}春花姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次见到你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就会真正把云雀变成我的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里就交给我处理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家先走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:03:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那怎么行！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道要把你一个人丢下么！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您莫非是在小看我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 应该说正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者结界！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}连我都不信任她了怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧 飞鸟！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:38.95,Chapter,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\bord2\blur5\1a&HFF\3c&H5A5760&\pos(1021,550)}决战天守阁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:38.95,Chapter,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\c&HE3EFED&\pos(1021,550)}决战天守阁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还真是个迷宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从这广大的校园来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比起我们学校还更恶劣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总之现在只有向前冲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真的曾经是半藏学院的学生么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么要当恶忍…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你应该去过忍者岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}“目标 超级忍者”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}“我要加油！”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是你在那的屋梁写的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎么知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是一看到你 我就突然看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那行字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然还朦朧模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但竟能将你培养至觉醒透视术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不愧是我的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我并没有学过那么厉害的忍术…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍术源于心术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}心灵的成长孕育忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍术的强弱取决于心灵的强弱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}铃音大人 您要做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}铃音老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}若有想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就该拼上性命去夺过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这才是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想要的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把我抓进结界进行决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您还真是信心满满啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您实在是事事令人不愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总是这样总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那座高山坡上的府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们这些贫苦的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直就在那座府邸蔑视的视线中活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}关于此次经由NPO法人进行的高额捐款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:18.44,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}注：NPO，非营利性组织(non-profit organization)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是住在那里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拯救世界上不幸的孩子们 也是企业的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的父母从未得到过什么救助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了养育我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甚至不惜付出了自己的性命！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}善忍 不要开玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}善忍的善 就是伪善的善
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你和你的家人就是那代表
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&H498615&}秘传忍法·尼福尔海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\bord5\fs36\pos(736,653)\3c&H498615&}Niflheim
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}应该直接命中她了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不惜以生命为代价依然疼爱你的这份家族爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}若是我曾拥有其千百分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也不会像这样痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也不能输！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}陷阱么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城姐 柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别过来 飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接下来就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}似乎再往上爬情况只会更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨蛋 你还在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这不是留了一个人在上面么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}陷阱没来得及发动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个叫飞鸟的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比想像中更敏捷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说得好像是别人的事似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然是你们的伏击么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正我也想找这家伙复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}暂且 先把她们收拾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你口气挺大的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打从第一次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就对你相当不爽！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别无视我！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者结界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者结界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和斑鸠用了一个套路倒是有点不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}随便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正我只要打败你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总算是不能再无视我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}守护我想守护之物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么那么想和我战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不打败你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就无法承认我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不能输给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我姑且忠告你一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忠告？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}边战斗边说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会咬到舌头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这双眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恐惧 悲伤 愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这些东西是致命的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把感情都抛掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}单单冷静地干掉目标
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就能活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么回事 看着这双眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像有什么被遗忘的东西受到了触动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你发什么呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这令人讨厌的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讨厌？我原来有这种感情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你自言自语个什么劲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放马过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不说我也会做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&H58915B&}秘传忍法·刺杀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上踢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也不能输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你以为我没有想要守护的东西么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}俺明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你明白了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}俺不知道你想保护什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但若是你在为此而战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就不无视我么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}否则就是否定了我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不对 这不是高兴的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&HF05BE5&}秘传忍法·女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\fs36\pos(741,651)\3c&HF05BE5&}Walkure
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}挺厉害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这上面就是顶层了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一个人么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小焰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我还以为会再多几个的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小云雀平安无事么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在牢房里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她在偷听结果被抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然小云雀是想一个人把忍法书夺回来才这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想要前进就打倒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半藏的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者结界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟 舞忍参上！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听到声音回来一看 果然不出所料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}春花姐 拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放我出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你出去准备干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得去和大家说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛇女的大家如果战败就会被施术杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不战胜我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们的目的也达不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但这和忍者的使命没有关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}确实没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们的容身之所只有这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前不是说过了么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都有各种各样的隐情才来这儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你刚刚说过地狱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那春花姐也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的父亲是大医院的院长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姑且不论他在社会上的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}背地里可是一个依靠逃税得来的收入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}掩盖数次医疗事故的恶劣之人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}父亲偶尔才回家一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就那种老生常谈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}母亲因此而萌生的不满
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}化为了对我的“溺爱”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}溺爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 才不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只不过是母亲的换装人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即便升上了中学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妈妈那异常的溺爱依然继续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然我一直闭口忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但终归我也渐渐觉得自己好像断了弦一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}燃尽一切 结束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}结束了…我就能重归自由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小孩子可不该玩火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}铃音老师似乎是打算发掘我所以一直在观察
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是有眼光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们一点也不怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为我们都是死过一次的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们是不是真的能打赢我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先由我来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正面上我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\blur8}忍·转身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我靠自己也会加油的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不会再让你担心了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者结界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}春花姐身上的忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一旦战败就会发动么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有点不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其实在施术者认为我们战败时发动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想 输赢有时候不是特别微妙么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那只要不让他发动就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我刚才也说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是不是能战胜我们这前提下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想太多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}重要的不是打赢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而是不要输
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不仅仅是不能输给对手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也不能输给自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&HAFB0DC&}秘传忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可不会败在同一招上两次！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大…大意了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能跟他们打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能打？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛇女们如果打输了就会失去性命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}性命！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她们被施了这种邪术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以不能和她们打！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如此强大的念话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这真是那个云雀做到的么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小焰…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打输了就会失去性命么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正确来说是叫做桎梏之术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小焰你们是在做好了觉悟的基础上才跟我们打的么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失败了就是死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这才是忍者原本的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么这样 这种事！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是不对的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是何等的残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正我们也不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪有这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}少开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那家伙真爱多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀她没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么对我一点话也没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刚不才说不无视我么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能与你们打了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抓住最上面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}施术的就是这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍法书也在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没想到你这么多嘴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&HDF9BF1&}秘传忍法·Death Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这次真要把你做成人偶了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&H5B5856&}秘传忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&H802CE4&}飞燕凤闪·一式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&HD17966&}Tornado Spinde
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得想办法上去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 要怎么才能上去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这么做对你们有什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拼上性命早有觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}将生死交由他人决定实在不对劲啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里是完全封闭…
Comment: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}究竟是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:21:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 上吧柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}俺要去地下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}地下？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀的声音是从地下传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}俺明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是么 云雀就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你究竟是什么时候有这种力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍术即心术
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.57,0:22:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是不惜对你们施以邪术强迫你们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.47,0:22:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}更为邪恶的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}邪恶？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}当我发现这一点的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的力量回应了我身为善忍的信条
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是说善忍都是老好人么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.43,0:22:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看到的那个电视节目
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目的是将父亲领养了我这件事公开于众
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}领养？难道说你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是“慈善家领养了举目无亲的孩子”这样的宣传
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事实上只是让我代替他没有忍法才能的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}继承忍者家系罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:23:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我仅有的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是身为忍者之使命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在使命里不曾包含一丁点家族的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.48,0:23:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么要和我说这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不就没法恨你了么！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.97,0:23:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}克服那些苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.96,0:23:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那些悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}与大家一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.08,0:23:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}守护到底！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟 忍舞参上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最终话 超秘传忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:40.02,Chapter,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,484)\bord2\blur3\shad1\c&HE2EEEE&\3c&H383A3B&}超秘传忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拼上性命来相夺吧
Comment: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,ED3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:22:02.17,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}それでいい　不連続な願望が心を導くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:07.87,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}走り続けて行くだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:25.23,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}はじめは　何も見えていない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:30.85,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}輝く意味すら分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:36.49,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}地中に埋もれた石のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:41.47,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}目を閉じ　夜明けを忍んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:45.37,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}ひりひりするような思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.37,0:22:50.16,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}息を殺しながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:53.62,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}舞い上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:59.73,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}私は走り続けてるから私だ　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:04.99,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}今日も明日も止まらない時の先へ　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.99,0:23:11.73,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}それでいい　不連続な願望が心を導くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.73,0:23:15.87,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}恐れなんて打ちのめして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:21.63,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}夢を走り続けていくだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:22:02.17,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}这样便好 若是断续的愿望能指引我的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:07.87,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}任我奔跑到底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:25.23,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}最初 什么也看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:30.85,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}甚至连閃耀的意义都不曾知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:36.49,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}庞若地里埋藏的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:41.47,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}闭上眼 直待天明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:45.37,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}回忆刺痛着我的神经
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.37,0:22:50.16,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}屏住呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:53.62,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}飞舞而上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:59.73,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}我奔跑故有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:04.99,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}不论今日明日都奔向那止不住的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.99,0:23:11.73,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}这样便好 若是断续的愿望能指引我的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.73,0:23:15.87,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}击败自身的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:21.63,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}向着梦想奔跑到底
